---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About — Teddy Wright">
  <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 pt-16 pb-16">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-8">About</h1>

    <div class="prose prose-gray max-w-none">
      <p>
        I'm Teddy Wright — a computer science student with a machine learning emphasis
        and economics minor, currently at BYU and transferring to the University of Utah's
        AI program in Fall 2026. I'm targeting a PhD in a space at the intersection of
        AI, human behavior, and information systems.
      </p>

      <p>
        My research sits at the intersection of AI capabilities and their human consequences:
        how LLMs reshape labor markets, why people form miscalibrated views about AI, and
        how we build tools and policy frameworks that account for the actual complexity of
        these systems.
      </p>

      <p>
        I work as a research assistant with Utah's Office of AI Policy, where I build
        data pipelines and interactive dashboards mapping AI's impact across occupations.
        I've also contributed to Project Iceberg, a nationally recognized AI labor market
        simulation study.
      </p>

      <p>
        Outside of research, I think a lot about identity formation, information processing,
        and what it means to rebuild a worldview from first principles. I write about these
        things sometimes. I also make music, watch anime, and run when I remember to.
      </p>

      <h2>Get in Touch</h2>
      <p>
        Email: <a href="mailto:teddyalanwright@gmail.com">teddyalanwright@gmail.com</a><br />
        Substack: <a href="https://substack.com/@theodorewright" target="_blank" rel="noopener">@theodorewright</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
